I'm **Farzana Hasan**, a GIA Expert. The competing cushion cut guides give you general advice without live 2026 price data, without the full crushed ice vs. chunky technical breakdown, without the color retention science, and without the complete proportion framework needed to evaluate a shape GIA does not grade. This guide provides all of it. Full credentials at **[Diamond Critics](https://diamondcritics.com/about-farzana/)**.

